AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore jak-remote
Account jak

MaildirStore jak-local
Path ~/Mail/jak/
Inbox ~/Mail/jak/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel jak
Far :jak-remote:
Near :jak-local:
Patterns *

